Find the best-rated Thai restaurant in Urbana, IL that serves duck cuisine on Google Maps. Review customer comments and compile a summary of positive and negative feedback in Notes.

---

raw_response:
### Thought ###
To find the best-rated Thai restaurant in Urbana, IL that serves duck cuisine, I will use Google Maps. I will search for Thai restaurants in Urbana, IL, filter the results by ratings, and check if they serve duck dishes by reviewing their menu or customer reviews. After identifying the best-rated restaurant, I will summarize the positive and negative feedback from customer reviews in the Notes app.

### Plan ###
1. Open the Google Maps app.
2. Search for "Thai restaurants in Urbana, IL."
3. Review the search results and identify the highest-rated restaurants.
4. Check the menu or customer reviews of the top-rated restaurants to confirm if they serve duck dishes.
5. Select the best-rated restaurant that serves duck cuisine.
6. Read customer reviews for the selected restaurant and summarize the positive and negative feedback.
7. Open the Notes app and record the summary.

### Current Subgoal ###
Open the Google Maps app.
